===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|speh₁}}
From {{etyl|eo|en}} {{m|eo|esperanto||one who hopes}}, from {{etyl|fr|en}} {{m|fr|espérer}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|sperare||to [[hope]]}}. Originally, this was the pseudonym assumed by the language's creator, L. L. Zamenhof, and the language was called {{m|eo|Lingvo Internacia||international language}}.

