===Etymology===
From the verb {{m|eo|esperi||to hope}}, which ultimately derives from {{etyl|la|eo}} {{m|la|sperare||to hope}}, and the affix [[-anto]]; meaning in Esperanto ''one who hopes''. ''Doktoro Esperanto'' ("Doctor Hopeful") was the pen-name of Esperanto's author, Dr. Zamenhof, when he published the language in 1887.

